### Minimal server health
GET http://localhost:3003/api/health

### List users with query string
GET http://localhost:3004/api/users?q=ali&limit=10

### Create a user
POST http://localhost:3004/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Charlie",
  "email": "charlie@example.com"
}

### Async config
GET http://localhost:3006/api/config

### Trigger centralized error handling
GET http://localhost:3006/api/fail

### Validate a good request
POST http://localhost:3007/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dana",
  "email": "dana@example.com",
  "age": 35
}

### Validate a bad request
POST http://localhost:3007/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "age": -1
}

### Capstone products
GET http://localhost:3010/api/products?q=node

### Create capstone product
POST http://localhost:3010/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Express Demo Pack",
  "category": "tool",
  "price": 29.99
}
